        <body>
            <div type="bibliography">
                
            </div>
            <div type="edition" xml:lang="gez">
                <note>This partial edition is based on <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/UppEt9">UppEt9</ref> 
                    as presented in
                    <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/X4SBAXAT"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Loefgren1974Katalog"/><title level="m">Katalog über die äthiopischen Handschriften in der Universitätsbibliothek Uppsala, Sowie Anhänge über äthiopische Handschriften in anderen Bibliotheken und in Privatbesitz in Schweden</title><title level="s">Acta Bibliothecae R. Universitatis Upsaliensis</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Oscar</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Löfgren</t:surname></author><pubPlace>Uppsala</pubPlace><publisher>Almqvist &amp; Wiksell</publisher><date>1974</date><series><t:title xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" level="s">Acta Bibliothecae R. Universitatis Upsaliensis</t:title><t:biblScope xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" unit="volume">18</t:biblScope></series><biblScope unit="volume">18</biblScope><citedRange unit="page">46–47</citedRange></bibl>
                    (original transcription by Augustine Dickinson).</note>
                <div type="textpart" xml:id="malke">
                    <lg type="stanza" n="1">
                        <l n="1">እግዚአብሔር፡ ለሰብእ፡ በከመ፡ ይቤ፡ ቀዲሙ፨</l>
                        <l n="2">እንዘ፡ ይከውነኒ፡ አፈ፡ ወጥበበ፡ ለለጌሰሙ፨</l>
                        <l n="3">ህሊናየሂ፡ እንዘ፡ እግድፍ፡ <unclear resp="PRS6337Lofgren">በእሙ</unclear>፨</l>
                        <l n="4">እዌጥን፡ ለዮስጦስ፡ ሰላመ፡ ክቡር፡ ስሙ፨</l>
                        <l n="5">በእንተ፡ ሥቃዩ፡ መንክር፡ ወዕፁብ፡ ሕማሙ፨</l>
                    </lg>
                    <lg type="stanza" n="2">
                        <l n="1"><supplied reason="undefined" resp="PRS6337Lofgren">ሰላም፡</supplied> 
                            ለዝክረ፡ ስምከ፡ በርእሰ፡ መጻሕፍት፡ ዘተጽሕፈ፨</l>
                        <l n="2">ከመ፡ ያንብብዎ፡ ሰብእ፡ እንዘ፡ ይከሥቱ፡ አፈ፨</l>
                        <l n="3">ክዱነ፡ አካል፡ ዮስጦስ፡ መብረቀ፡ ስብሐት፡ አጽፈ፨</l>
                        <l n="4">ዕቀበነ፡ ወትረ፡ እምጸላኢ፡ ወተማኅፀነነ፡ ዘልፈ፨</l>
                        <l n="5">ከመ፡ ጸላኢ፡ ኢይምላሕ፡ በላዕሌነ፡ ሰይፈ፨</l>
                    </lg>
                    <lg type="stanza" n="50">
                        <l n="1"><supplied reason="undefined" resp="PRS6337Lofgren">ሰላም፡</supplied> 
                            ለመቃብሪከ፡ ለአ<supplied reason="undefined" resp="PRS6337Lofgren">ስ</supplied>ከሬነ፡ ወርቅ፡ ዘመሰሎ፨</l>
                        <l n="2">ውስቴቱ፡ ሥጋከ፡ እስመ፡ ከመ፡ ወርቅ፡ ሀሎ፨</l>
                        <l n="3">ተሣሀለኒ፡ ዮስጦስ፡ እስመ፡ በጽሐ፡ ጊዜ፡ ተሣህሎ፨</l>
                        <l n="4">ወክፍል፡ ታእድወነ፡ ማእበለ፡ ዘመን፡ ተኃጕሎ፨</l>
                        <l n="5">ከመ፡ ለዮር<sic resp="JK">ደ</sic>ኖስ፡ በሐሜለቱ፡ ኤልያስ፡ ከፈሎ፨</l>
                    </lg>
                    <lg type="stanza" n="51">
                        <l n="1">ስብሐተ፡ ማኅሌት፡ ወሀቡ፡ ለመልክዕከ፡ በኍልቍ፨</l>
                        <l n="2">በእንተ፡ ዝኒ፡ ሰአሎ፡ ውስተ፡ <supplied reason="undefined" resp="PRS6337Lofgren">አስ</supplied>ተብቍኦ፡ በሕቁ፨</l>
                        <l n="3">ለእግዚአብሔር፡ ዮስጦስ፡ ቅድመ፡ በተጽናስ፡ ይሕልቁ፨</l>
                        <l n="4">ብዑላነ፡ ከመ፡ <unclear resp="PRS6337Lofgren">ይከት፡</unclear> ለተክለ፡ ሀይማኖት፡ ደቂቁ፨</l>
                        <l n="5">በጽድቁ፡ ለአርያም፡ ወለምድር፡ በወርቁ፨</l>
                    </lg>
                </div>
                    <div type="textpart" xml:id="tarafa-malke" n="1">
                        <lg type="stanza" n="1">
                        <l n="1">ሰላም፡ ለከ፡ መሠረታቲሃ፡ ለጽዮን፡ ውቅተ፡ ቅዱሳን፡ አድባር፨</l>
                        <l n="2">አስተጻንዕ፡ ለነ፡ እምሁከተ፡ ምድር፨</l>
                        <l n="3">ዮስጦስ፡ እብነ፡ ሰንፔር፨</l>
                    </lg>
                    </div>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text></TEI>